    "content": [
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "A tapping script for Day 15 of the money arc. The script works with the guilt that can surface when you want wealth, the worry that wanting more makes you greedy or selfish, and the belief that desire is a character flaw.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "New to tapping? Read ",
            "type": "text"
          },
          {
            "text": "how EFT tapping works",
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "link",
                "attrs": {
                  "href": "/mindset/how-eft-tapping-works"
                }
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "text": " first.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "The practice",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Karate chop",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "bulletList",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "text": "Even though part of me feels guilty for wanting more money, I deeply and completely accept myself.",
                    "type": "text"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "text": "Even though I sometimes think wealth is selfish, I deeply and completely accept myself.",
                    "type": "text"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "text": "Even though I worry people will judge me for wanting financial freedom, I deeply and completely accept myself.",
                    "type": "text"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Tapping round",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "bulletList",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "text": "Eyebrow:",
                    "type": "text",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "bold"
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "text": " I've been told that wanting wealth is greedy.",
                    "type": "text"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "text": "Side of eye:",
                    "type": "text",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "bold"
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "text": " Part of me feels guilty just for wanting this.",
                    "type": "text"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "text": "Under eye:",
                    "type": "text",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "bold"
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "text": " I worry it means I don't care about others.",
                    "type": "text"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "text": "Under nose:",
                    "type": "text",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "bold"
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "text": " I fear people will think less of me for wanting more.",
                    "type": "text"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "text": "Chin:",
                    "type": "text",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "bold"
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "text": " I've been hiding how much I want.",
                    "type": "text"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "text": "Collarbone:",
                    "type": "text",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "bold"
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "text": " I feel torn between desire and guilt.",
                    "type": "text"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "text": "Under arm:",
                    "type": "text",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "bold"
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "text": " I'm tired of pretending I don't want more.",
                    "type": "text"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "text": "Top of head:",
                    "type": "text",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "bold"
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "text": " I'm ready to see this differently.",
                    "type": "text"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
